\newlabel{tab:yolo-stats}{{7}{4}{Per-camera detection statistics. ``Coverage'' is the fraction of source frames with at least one detection. ``Low-conf kp'' is the fraction of individual keypoint observations with $\text {conf} < 0.35$ (the value that the downstream pipeline treats as missing)}{table.7}{}}
